| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1168 — Recovery Inhibition (direwolf)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b70cbc86-28ce-55af-a39c-e14e3a5f2d95"
